Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:39.94,logo2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SGS曙光社\Nhttp://bbs.sgsub.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵体受到伤害的话 对契约者也会有影响么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说 杀了灵体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 艾丽丝…不要再打了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是 那个孩子的 菲力普的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说梦话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我挥起利刃的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用死亡来偿还吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗 我无法阻止艾丽丝吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来 你可以避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有这样的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一击!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 艾丽丝～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了 我的力量被抑制了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 我说过你可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur7}重叠的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…爸爸出事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经三天没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 像这样的情况以前也有过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸一定会回家的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想变成孤身一人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力普
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把你父亲带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…觉得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起父亲时是那样的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…比起以前能更多的呆在爸爸身边了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子和我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为这么想着才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这样的事 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会和灵体签订契约?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经有了菲力普 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么和灵体签订契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了菲力普啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了菲力普要改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候要是没有在契约书上签字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家族也不会没落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是那个庸医 妻子就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有相信那些人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会落到如此悲惨的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切 一切的一切都不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一切可以重来 菲力普一定能幸福!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做有什么错？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了菲力普…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我是为了儿子才杀人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子…你说儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我自己的话怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是菲力普只是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有让儿子…让那孩子幸福的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样下去菲力普会变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法接受! 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…是真的这么想的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了菲力普的话什么都能做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又了解我什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不了解你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:08:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不呆在菲力普的身旁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能和菲力普在一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是你儿子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不想变成孤身一人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…不是他父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔巴特在地下室反省
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷还说少爷暂时不能出门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让我孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有必要改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要能对他说「没关系…留在我身边就好」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你呆在身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样…菲力普就能幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力普也拿着的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力普
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少…再和那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少…再和那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧 菲力普
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把你父亲带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…我没开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是…菲力普的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪的是我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…这孩子刚刚差点被杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个男人 无论是活着还是死着堕入阿嵬茨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有存活的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 这个也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法的事呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受我之主 文森特大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来带走这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过来时乘的马车还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…还在哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让奥兹到安全的地方休养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向菲力普…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么也不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是基尔的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然在所不辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚打扰真是抱歉 兰兹华斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 请不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔说不要回奈特雷依家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹别扭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…这就要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还想好好和基尔聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也有事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…我和基尔不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似不怎么受欢迎呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你到玄关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是多谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是老样子冷冰冰的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是应该说他不够坦率呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这样害羞正是他可爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间有着血缘的羁绊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护主人是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他却…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的奋不顾身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真在乎奥兹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你现在必须做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是其他的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一切可以重来 菲力普一定能幸福!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的父亲 为了菲力普的话什么都能做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 因为这个而杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的孩子 要是没有出生就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肮脏的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不需要我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要到哪里才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得孤身一人活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让菲力普拥有着和我一样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也…有那样生气的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你呆在身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗 像变了一个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不大明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道自己在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对那孩子 对菲力普说过会带他父亲回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而却什么也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人本来就是无法解救的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海藻头不是也说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再管这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说放就放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到那个孩子现在一定也孤身一人等待着父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂你到底在烦恼什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子会怎样 说实话我也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人会觉得冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定因为那孩子会留下冷寂的回忆而悲伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你这件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算去潘多拉么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事想调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我个人的猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的格里姆逃跑事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有潘多拉的人做内应的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是怕格里姆泄露某些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不被发现是内部所为而放走他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人不知鬼不觉消灭它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是伪装成事故再杀了它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}为了救这孩子没办法只好杀了它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸如此类的…理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是可怕呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到组织里存在着这样的背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要担心哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真有这样的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论这个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会亲手揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}你只要利用我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}若能再次取回那道光……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.72,0:23:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}即使沉浸在感伤里 也无法改变什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}只会错失真相而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}背叛少爷的事我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}所有的点与点联结在一起—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}最终将归结于一处……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&}下回 堕落的鸦
